湖北现有疑似清零。
Hubei is suspected of Qingnil.
多省发现回国人员中存在无症状感染者，“外防输入”形势仍然较为严峻。
Many provinces found that there were asymptomatic infection among the returnees, "external defense input" situation is still more severe.
美国新增迅速逼近2000例。
The United States is rapidly approaching 2,000 new cases.
美、韩均计划直接向民众发放现金以度过困难时期文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图 |《财经》视觉中心编辑|郝洲一、国内新增仅1例，现多起“无症状”输入病例图1今日国内简述：国内3月17日报告累计确诊病例80894例，武汉新增1例。
The United States and South Korea plan to send cash directly to the public to tide them through difficult times. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
湖北现有疑似病例清零。
Suspected case cleared in Hubei.
新增报告境外输入确诊病例12例（广东5例，北京3例，上海3例，四川1例）。
A total of 12 confirmed cases were reported from abroad (5 in Guangdong, 3 in Beijing, 3 in Shanghai and 1 in Sichuan).
山东、四川、云南、贵州多省均发现回国人员中存在无症状感染者，“外防输入”形势仍然较为严峻。
Shandong, Sichuan, Yunnan and Guizhou provinces all found asymptomatic infection among the returnees, and the situation of "external defense input" is still serious.
二、世卫组织呼吁各国采取“最大胆的行动”图2海外新增病例进一步扩大，达到15721例。
WHO Calls on Countries to Take "Bold Action" Figure 2 New cases overseas have expanded to 15,721.
紧随意大利之后，德国、西班牙、美国新增均在2000例左右。
After Italy, Germany, Spain and the United States all added about 2,000 new cases.
世界卫生组织欧洲区域办事处主任汉斯·克鲁格在记者会上说：“每个国家，无一例外，都需要采取最大胆的行动，以阻止或减缓（新冠）病毒的威胁。
"Every country, without exception, needs to take the bolder action to stop or mitigate the threat of the virus," Hans Kruger, director of the WHO Regional Office for Europe, told a news conference.
”俄罗斯政府决定从3月18日至5月1日禁止所有外国公民和无国籍人士入境。
The Russian government decided to ban all foreign nationals and stateless persons from March 18 to May 1.
图3美国这艘“航天飞机”似乎终于注满燃料了，自疫情以来，单日增幅首次破千，并迅速向2000迈进。
Fig. 3 The U. S. space shuttle appears to have finally filled up with fuel, breaking through for the first time in a day since the outbreak, and making rapid progress toward 2000.
德国也在预料之中走上了快车道。
Germany, too, was on the fast track as expected.
三、全美50个州和华盛顿哥伦比亚特区全部“中招”图4美国出现了自疫情以来最大增幅，单日新增确诊病例 1764例，累计确诊病例达到6461例，较前一日增长37.6%。
Figure 4 shows the largest increase since the outbreak in the United States, with 1,764 new cases confirmed a day and a cumulative total of 6,461 confirmed cases, an increase of 37.6 percent over the previous day.
美国西维吉尼亚州首次发现确诊病例。
The first confirmed case was found in West Virginia.
至此，全美50个州和华盛顿哥伦比亚特区全部“中招”。
So far, all 50 states and Washington, D.C., have made it.
当地时间3月17日，美国政府宣布将推出一揽子经济刺激计划，以缓解疫情对市场和经济的冲击，该计划的总价值可能在1万亿美元左右，这是有史以来规模最大的联邦紧急财政计划之一。
On March 17, the U.S. government announced that it would launch a stimulus package to cushion the market and economy from the epidemic, possibly worth about $1 trillion, one of the largest federal emergency fiscal programs ever.
同时，美国政府有意在两周内向美国人发放支票，每人将得到1000美元的补贴。
Meanwhile, the U.S. government intends to issue cheques to Americans within two weeks, each receiving a $1,000 subsidy.
四、欧洲多国跟进封锁，意大利万名医学毕业生提前毕业图5英国首相鲍里斯·约翰逊和财政大臣瑞希·苏纳克3月17日下午联合出席发布会。
European nations follow up on the embargo with Italy's 10,000 medical graduates graduating early. British Prime Minister Boris Johnson and Chancellor of the Exchequer Rexi Sunak jointly attended a press conference on the afternoon of March 17.
对于扶持危机中的中小企业，英国政府推将出一系列紧急的救助计划，包括拨款3300亿英镑用来满足企业的信贷资金需求。
The U.K. government is rolling out a range of emergency programs to help small and medium-sized enterprises in crisis, including GBP 330 billion to meet their credit needs.
英国政府首席科学顾问帕特里克·瓦伦斯承认，英国目前尚未对全部感染者进行病毒检测，只能对症状严重的感染者优先检测。
Patrick Vallance, chief science adviser to the British government, admitted that all infected people in the UK were not tested for the virus and only those with severe symptoms were given priority.
在世卫组织发出警示和提醒后，英国决定加大检测力度。
Following warnings and reminders from the WHO, the UK decided to step up testing.
瓦伦斯希望，通过积极医疗干预，英国的死亡病患总数可能会在2万人以内。
Varens hopes that with aggressive medical intervention, the total number of deaths in the UK could be as low as 20,000.
从当地时间3月17日开始，瑞士全境进入“紧急状态”，除基础服务设施外，其余公共场所和设施一律停业。
A "state of emergency" has been in force throughout Switzerland since March 17, when all but basic services have been shut down.
挪威政府决定将没有居留权的人驱逐出境，以减少新冠肺炎的传播感染。
The Norwegian government has decided to deport people without residency to reduce the spread of new crown pneumonia.
爱尔兰全国已经建起19个专门的新冠病毒检测中心，接受检测的人员可以进行不下车病毒感染检测。
Nineteen dedicated Crown Virus testing centres have been set up across Ireland, where people can be tested for non-alight virus infections.
卢森堡首相3月17日宣布该国进入为期3个月的紧急状态，这在卢森堡历史上尚属首次。
For the first time in Luxembourg's history, the Prime Minister of Luxembourg declared a three-month state of emergency on 17 March.
图6为了帮助卫生服务部门应对新型冠状病毒疫情，意大利大学部长加埃塔诺·曼弗雷迪称，政府将让今年的医学院毕业生提前八至九个月开始工作，并免除他们获得从业资格前的强制考试。
Fig. 6 To help health services respond to the new coronavirus epidemic, Italian University Minister Gaetano Manfredi said the government would allow medical school graduates this year to start working eight to nine months early and exempt them from mandatory pre-qualification examinations.
“这意味着立即向国家卫生系统输送约1万名医生，对于缓解我国正在遭受的医生短缺情况至关重要。
"This means that the immediate delivery of some 10,000 doctors to the national health system is essential to alleviate the shortage of doctors that the country is experiencing.
”五、韩国治愈率18.3%，连续4日新增两位数以内图7截至3月18日，韩国新冠肺炎患者中1540例已治愈并解除隔离，治愈率达18.3%。
Fig. 7 As of March 18, 1540 cases of pneumonia in South Korea had been cured and unquarantined, with a cure rate of 18.3 percent.
为进一步防控新冠疫情，韩国国会17日深夜通过了规模达11.7万亿韩元（约合人民币663.3405亿元）的追加预算案。
South Korea's parliament approved a supplementary budget of 11.7 trillion won (66,334.05 million yuan) in the middle of the night to further control the outbreak.
具体来看，该预算案为疫情重点地区大邱市和庆尚北道编制1.0394万亿韩元；为个体工商户增编1.1638万亿韩元的预算；为应对疫情增编1483亿韩元，为稳定民生增编7696亿韩元；为低成本航空公司等受到疫情冲击的行业增编2418亿韩元。
Specifically, the budget provides 1.0394 trillion won for Daegu city and Gyeongshan North Province, 1.0394 trillion won for individual businesses, 14.83 billion won for individual businesses, 769.6 billion won for people's livelihood, and 241.8 billion won for industries hit by the epidemic, such as low-cost airlines.
韩国首尔市为因新冠肺炎而直接受到打击的市民提供"灾难紧急生活费"。
Seoul, South Korea, has AT & quot; & quot; & quot; disaster emergency & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot;
对117.7万户中低收入家庭给予补贴，每户补贴30万-50万韩元。
Subsidies were granted to 1.177 million low- and middle-income families, with subsidies ranging from 300,000 to 500,000 won per household.
首尔市市长朴元淳表示:"这是为了克服国家危机,搞活地区经济的举措。
Park Yuanchun, Seoul's mayor, said: & quot; It was a move to overcome the country's crisis and revitalize the region's economy.
"六、伊朗关闭两处什叶派圣地，释放8.5万名囚犯图8伊朗什叶派圣城马什哈德和库姆则破天荒关闭了两处圣地，引发民众激烈抗议。
Iran has shut down two Shiite holy sites and released 85,000 prisoners. Iran's Shiite holy cities of Mashhad and Qom have closed two holy sites for the first time, sparking fierce protests.
除了关闭宗教场所，伊朗卫生部官员已多次呼吁民众留在家中，不要随意出门，警告“现在为准备新年出门采购相当于自杀”。
In addition to shutting down places of worship, Iranian Health Ministry officials have repeatedly called on people to stay at home and not to go out, warning that "going shopping now for the New Year is tantamount to suicide."
但很多民众依然无视警告，各地的商场和餐馆依然照常营业。
But many people continue to ignore warnings that shopping malls and restaurants remain open everywhere.
为防止疫情进一步扩散，伊朗司法部于3月17日再度宣布释放包括政治犯在内的8.5万名囚犯。
To prevent further spread of the epidemic, on 17 March the Iranian Ministry of Justice again announced the release of 85,000 prisoners, including political prisoners.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】七、全球疫情数字速览：1、【20亿美元研发疫苗】流行病防范创新联盟CEO理查德·哈切特估算，要足够快地开发出新冠肺炎疫苗，需要在未来12到18个月内花费20亿美元。
According to the latest statistics, the WHO official statistics dated February 28 are due at 17: 00 daily Beijing time. Starting on Feb. 28, data from Caijing daily according to open data have been closed at 9: 00pm daily.
2、【100万人失业】美国白宫经济顾问委员会前主席哈塞特（Kevin Hassett）接受媒体采访时称，在疫情影响下，出现全球经济衰退的可能性接近100%。
2007-9-24 15: 23 [hide] "Kevin Hassett, former chairman of the White House Council of Economic Advisers, said in a media interview that the possibility of a global recession under the impact of the epidemic was close to 100 percent.
美国3月最多可能有100万人失业。
Up to one million people could be out of work in the US in March.
美国此前最大的失业危机发生在2009年3月，一个月内失业人数高达80万人。
The largest unemployment crisis in the United States occurred in March 2009, when 800,000 people were unemployed in one month.
小结：湖北现有疑似清零。
Summary: Hubei existing suspected Qingnil.
多省发现回国人员中存在无症状感染者，“外防输入”形势仍然较为严峻。
Many provinces found that there were asymptomatic infection among the returnees, "external defense input" situation is still more severe.
美国新增迅速逼近2000例。
The United States is rapidly approaching 2,000 new cases.
美、韩均计划直接向民众发放现金以度过困难时期。
Both the United States and South Korea plan to send cash directly to the public to tide them over difficult times.
意大利让万名医学生提前毕业，加入抗疫大军。
Italy has allowed tens of thousands of medical students to graduate early to join the fight against the disease.
